A hero-power, or hero-god, is a Power that has attained enough power and followers to grant spells. They are a step above Quasi-deity and a step below demi-god in the Power Hierarchy. They tend to have very narrow portfolios. Some of the better known hero-powers are Keoghtom, Murlynd, Kuroth, Kyuss, Nazarn, Roykyn, Tsolorandril, Azor'alq, Charmalaine, Daern, Daoud, Diancastra, Gadhelyn, Gendwar Argrim, Johydee, Zinzerena, Kelanen and Vathris. 

